{"tid":2071851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明日香港：許志永因討論時政被捕 不知罪名去向下落","createTime":"2020-06-20T07:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T07:34:19.000Z","uid":7542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0c367024fc34551dc35a86387281ce9df4e27b","tid":2071851,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"內地著名維權人士許志永被當局批准逮捕，但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">未有向家人透露許志永涉及的罪名和羈押地點</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>許志永與多名維權人士去年12月初在廈門參與聚會，討論時政和國家的未來，其後參與聚會的人士被指<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>煽動顛覆國家</ins></span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n許志永今年2月15日在廣東被捕，被帶走時公安口頭通知涉嫌煽動顛覆國家政權罪行，並會實施指定居所監視居住。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533148-20200620.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533148-20200620.htm&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=f7ed4f69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533148-20200620.htm&h=d1c82999\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533148-20200620.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ea46143c948b60a8fb4ef565dbdc3e11a844195c","tid":2071851,"uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:14:17.000Z","msg":"[size=5]<strong>又係時候 share 下</strong>[/size=4] <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF-SKS89xxRg&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=8ba15241\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BufF8VPWDZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBufF8VPWDZg&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=60cc2689\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BufF8VPWDZg</a><br />\n